Name: Paperboo
Desc: Always nostalgic over when it hatched from its shell.

1.Name: Decoy Paper Armor
1.Desc:
<color=#FFFFFF>Active Skill</color>
Uses a cardboard box to camouflage itself, inducing a taunt effect: While camouflaged, being attacked by enemies or reaching the camouflage time limit will trigger an explosion, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color> in an area.

1.Name: Cardboard Armor
1.Desc:
<color=#FFFFFF>Additional Ability</color>
When there is at least 1 <color=#FFFFFF>Defense</color> character in your squad: <color=#FFFFFF>Bangboo Chain Attack</color> generates Shield for all squad members. The more enemies hit, the more Shield generated, up to a max of 15% of Paperboo's Max HP.
